        <scene id="10" background="westCliffBossRoom.jpg">
            <bgm src="horror.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <show chara="ritaAgentClose-up" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ritaNoFace">我是“女侯爵”。</speak>
            <speak chara="ritaNoFace">本想招待一下“亚当”，没想到却跟着来了“乔治”。</speak>
            <speak chara="ritaNoFace">应当如何准备“主菜”，请指示。</speak>
            <goto goto="20" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="20" background="westCliffDinnerRoom.jpg">
            <bgm src="10_20_PeerGynt.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <show chara="fuhuaEatBack" position="back"/>
            <show chara="teslaEatGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <show chara="einSmileCoatClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">哇！好丰盛！都分不清哪个才是主菜了呢！</speak>
            <show chara="teslaEatGlassWinterClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einSmileCoatClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">……不着急，慢慢吃。</speak>
            <show chara="einSmileCoatClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltDarkSweaterClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">……</speak>
            <show chara="weltDarkSweaterClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="teslaEatGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">怎么了你……没精打采的。</speak>
            <show chara="teslaEatGlassWinterClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltDarkSweaterClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">我……</speak>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">我无法阻止自己，不去想三年前的柏林。</speak>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">卡尔……</speak>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">玛莎……</speak>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">像他们这样无辜的人……</speak>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">……在那一天，还有三十万。</speak>
            <show chara="weltShameSweaterClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">三十万啊！</speak>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">这得是什么样的一个概念？</speak>
            <show chara="weltShameSweaterClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="teslaBoringGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">……</speak>
            <show chara="teslaSmileGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">你就应该和我在一起，傻瓜。</speak>
            <show chara="teslaSmileGlassWinterClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseSweaterClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">？？？</speak>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseSweaterClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="teslaSmileGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">我们的人生都没有什么值得回忆的……</speak>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">……不需要为过去再留恋什么。</speak>
            <show chara="teslaShameGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">While worldly matters take their turn, （人世有代谢）</speak>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">Ancient, modern, to and fro, （往来成古今）</speak>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">Rivers and mountains are changeless in their glory （江山留胜迹）</speak>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">And still to be witnessed from this trail. （我辈复登临）</speak>
            <show chara="teslaSnickerGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">——这是东方诗人孟浩然的诗句。</speak>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">你懂汉语……所以，大概比我更能理解其中的意味吧。</speak>
            <show chara="weltDarkSweaterClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">……</speak>
            <show chara="weltDarkSweaterClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="teslaBoringGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">或许你在今后的人生中，还会听到很多，柏林事件遇难者的故事。</speak>
            <show chara="teslaNormalGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">无论如何……请不要擅自把他们的过去，和你自己的未来嫁接在一起。</speak>
            <show chara="teslaShameGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">毫无疑问，你既是个幸运儿，又是个倒霉蛋——</speak>
            <show chara="teslaSnickerGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">但你不欠他们什么；他们也不欠你什么。</speak>
            <show chara="teslaSmileGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">你自己的人生，你自己问心无愧就好。</speak>
            <show chara="teslaSmileGlassWinterClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltDarkSweaterClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">……</speak>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">…………</speak>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">………………</speak>
            <show chara="weltGiggleSweaterClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">嗯。</speak>
            <show chara="weltGiggleSweaterClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="teslaSnickerGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">嗯。这就对嘛。</speak>
            <show chara="teslaSmileGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">好孩子~好孩子~~</speak>
            <show chara="teslaEatGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">来，吃肉吃肉~~~</speak>
            <show chara="teslaEatGlassWinterClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einSmileCoatClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">特斯拉……</speak>
            <show chara="einSmileCoatClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="teslaShameGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">干嘛……</speak>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">还不快夸奖我？</speak>
            <show chara="teslaShameGlassWinterClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einSlyCoatClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">噗……</speak>
            <show chara="einSlyCoatClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="teslaShameGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">怎、怎么啦……人、人家偶尔也是会正直一下的嘛！</speak>
            <show chara="teslaShameGlassWinterClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einSlyCoatClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">……真可爱呢，特斯拉小姐。</speak>
            <show chara="einSlyCoatClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="teslaShoutGlassWinterClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">可、可爱是什么意思啦！</speak>
            <goto goto="30" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="30" background="westCliff.jpg">
            <bgm src="10_20_PeerGynt.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <text>虽然享用午餐的客人，看起来只有寥寥几人——</text>
            <text remark="next">但“西崖·丽塔”提供的食材，从鹅肝到牡蛎，从牛里脊到海螯虾……</text>
            <remark>
                <p class="article-text-h">注：</p>
                <p class="article-text">海螯虾（Lobster）是一种大型海洋虾类，分布广泛，常被人误称为龙虾（Palinuridae）。</p>
                <p class="article-text">海螯虾和龙虾的主要区别包括：海螯虾有一对大“钳子”，龙虾没有；海螯虾触角又细又短，龙虾的触角长、粗、多刺；海螯虾在世界各地都有分布，龙虾只分布在热带、亚热带地区。</p>
            </remark>
            <text>各种肉类可谓一应俱全，简直丰富到了让人不好意思的程度。</text>
            <show chara="teslaEatGlassWinterClose-up" position="center" opacity="0.8"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">你们！不觉得内心惭愧吗？！</speak>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">不把这些全都吃光抹净，怎么能对得起辛苦采购它们的老板娘呢？！</speak>
            <show chara="teslaEatGlassWinterClose-up" position="center" opacity="0"/>
            <text>于是，在这午后三点、日光正舒适的时刻，实践了自己那番豪言壮语的某人，只能像海豹一样平摊在自己的大床上。</text>
            <show chara="teslaAstonishDrunkWinterClose-up" position="center" opacity="0.8"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">散步？</speak>
            <show chara="teslaNormalDrunkWinterClose-up" position="center" opacity="0.8"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">这种老年人一样的运动，不要叫我啦……</speak>
            <show chara="teslaAstonishDrunkWinterClose-up" position="center" opacity="0.8"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">保龄球？不不不……我现在是无论如何也打不了那个啊……</speak>
            <show chara="teslaNormalDrunkWinterClose-up" position="center" opacity="0.8"/>
            <speak chara="teslaNoFace">你们去散步吧……我等会自己泡个温泉缓一缓……</speak>
            <show chara="teslaEatGlassWinterClose-up" position="center" opacity="0"/>
            <text>不过，话说回来……</text>
            <text>比起“把自己吃进医院里”的黑历史，这好歹也算是一种进步了？</text>
            <goto goto="40" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="40" background="westCliffBeach.jpg">
            <bgm src="themeWelt.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <show chara="fuhuaWatchingSeaBack" position="back"/>
            <text>冬季，大概是天际线离我们最近的时候。</text>
            <text remark="next">阴冷潮湿的海滩、锈迹斑斑的海洋堡垒、拉着浓烟的各式轮船——这便是全部的视野。</text>
            <remark>
                <p class="article-text-h">注：</p>
                <p class="article-text">默恩塞尔海洋堡垒（Maunsell Forts）是二战时期英国修筑在泰晤士河、默西河河口的量产型防空塔。</p>
                <p class="article-text">海洋堡垒的结构类似于陆地上的高射炮阵地，区别是它们像高脚楼一样修筑在混凝土驳船上。堡垒在船坞中组装好后，由拖船拖往指定海域，然后令混凝土驳船自沉，将堡垒基座稳固地锚定在海底。</p>
                <p class="article-text">二战后，堡垒被废弃。其中，位于萨福克郡以东公海内的“怒涛塔”（HMS Fort Rough）在1967年9月2日被退伍军人迪·罗伊·贝茨（Paddy Roy Bates）一家“占领”，并声称根据国际法“独立”为“西兰公国”（Principality of Sealand）。虽然其声明被国际社会认为没有合法性，但也确实成为了国际法应用中的一个有趣个案。</p>
            </remark>
            <text>沧桑，孤寂，令人平静。</text>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left"/>
            <show chara="einSmileWinterFar" position="center" opacity="0.7"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">啊。</speak>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einSmileWinterFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">嗯？</speak>
            <show chara="einSmileWinterFar" position="center" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">那边的那个人……刚才吃饭的时候，好像见过？</speak>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einNormalWinterFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">是……怎么了？</speak>
            <show chara="einNormalWinterFar" position="center" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">……我也说不上。</speak>
            <show chara="weltGiggleWinterFar" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">就是总有一股……“这个人很危险”的感觉……</speak>
            <show chara="weltGiggleWinterFar" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="fuhuaWatchingYouBack" position="back"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">……</speak>
            <show chara="weltShameWinterFar" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">（糟糕……她不会是听见了？）</speak>
            <show chara="weltShameWinterFar" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <hide position="back"/>
            <hide position="center"/>
            <show chara="fuhuaNormalOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">……</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileCloseEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">水落鱼梁浅，</speak>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">天寒梦泽深。</speak>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">羊公碑尚在，</speak>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">读罢泪沾襟。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">这是之前那首诗的后半阙——你能听懂汉语吧？</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileOpenEyeFar" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">只能说懂一点……</speak>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">……您是东方人？</speak>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileCloseEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">算是吧。从这里的角度看，神州的确是“东方”。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">啊，对了。这本书就送你吧。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileOpenEyeFar" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">送、送我？</speak>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="fuhuaNormalOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">没什么，一本诗集罢了。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">看完了，你也可以像我刚才那样，现学现卖。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileOpenEyeFar" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltNormalWinterFar" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">可、可是……</speak>
            <show chara="weltNormalWinterFar" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileCloseEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">没什么。我也就是一时兴起乱买的。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaNormalCloseEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">最近脑子里的东西已经太多了，其实根本装不下这种乱七八糟的知识。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">况且……</speak>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">……能让它跨越半个地球，来到你的手上，这不也是一种缘分么？</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileOpenEyeFar" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">缘分……吗。</speak>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="fuhuaNormalOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">嗯。</speak>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">比如，刚才那首诗，《与诸子登岘山》。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaNormalCloseEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">从地理上看，岘山不过是神州腹地的一个小土丘。比不了五岳，比不了雪山，比不了世界屋脊。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSeriousFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">但是有位朋友告诉过我，这小小的岘山，却是“龙脉”相交、关乎神州安危的关键之处。</speak>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">传说中，神州始祖之一，伏羲，就埋葬在那里——用她自己的身体，镇守“龙脉”，守护那片土地。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSeriousFar" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einNormalWinterFar" position="back"/>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">……瓦尔特，能翻译一下她在说什么吗？</speak>
            <show chara="einNormalWinterFar" position="back" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">唔……就是想把这本诗集送我……还讲了一个东方的传说故事……</speak>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="fuhuaNormalCloseEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">Nein, ist es nicht.（不，不是的。）</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaNormalOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">这不是什么传说。</speak>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">所谓“龙脉”，用今天的话说，就是崩坏能自然泄漏形成的“暗河”。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaNormalCloseEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">传说总是有它的由来的。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaNormalCloseEyeFar" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einSeriousAhWinterFar" position="back"/>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">你……是什么人？</speak>
            <show chara="einSeriousEmWinterFar" position="back" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="fuhuaNormalOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoNameNoFace">女武神·符华。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileCloseEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoFace">算是你们认识的蕾安娜的同事吧。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoFace">她对你们的评价很不错哦？</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileOpenEyeFar" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">呃……谢谢……？</speak>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="fuhuaNormalOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoFace">今天你们也许会遇到一个有点麻烦的危险人物。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileCloseEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoFace">不过别担心——至少我能保证，不会有任何危及人身安全的事情发生。</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoFace">Adieu.（再见了。）</speak>
            <hide position="back"/>
            <show chara="fuhuaNormalOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoFace">（瓦尔特先生。）</speak>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileCloseEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoFace" remark="next">（中文）相濡以沫，不如相忘于江湖。</speak>
            <remark>
                <p class="article-text-h">注：</p>
                <p class="article-text">本句出自《庄子·内篇·大宗师》：“泉涸，鱼相与处于陆，相呴以湿，相濡以沫，不如相忘于江湖。”</p>
                <p class="article-text">庄子是借此表达：与其在艰难困苦中同舟共济，不如从一开始就杜绝灾难的发生，太平无事。</p>
            </remark>
            <show chara="fuhuaSmileOpenEyeFar" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="fuhuaNoFace">未来的事情……愿你们好自为之。</speak>
            <hide position="right"/>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">……</speak>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="einNormalWinterFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="einNoFace">……奇怪的人。</speak>
            <show chara="einNormalWinterFar" position="center" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltSurpriseWinterFar" position="left"/>
